  "stem": "<p>The expression (5<i>x</i> &minus; 17)(13<i>x</i> + 8) is equivalent to the expression <i>a</i><i>x</i>&sup2; + <i>b</i><i>x</i> + <i>c</i>, where <i>a</i>, <i>b</i>, and <i>c</i> are constants. What is the value of <i>b</i>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": null,
